nodes.text: A memory core manufacturing plant stood in the Alien Protection Zone of Imperial Center in 7 ABY. Agents of the planet's Alien Combine in cooperation with the New Republic's Rogue Squadron entered one of the plant's warehouses posing as employees in an attempt to slip rigged memory cores into Imperial Center's central computer system. Their purpoted ally from Black Sun, Zekka Thyne, sold them out, and an arriving group of Imperial stormtroopers engaged them in a lightfight.
